    <p class="mt-3"><span class="text-color">4)</span> Sur une échelle de 10 évaluez votre expérience et vos compétences entrepreneuriales:<span class="text-danger">*</span></p>
    <span id="params_answer_team_4"><%=params[:answer_team_4]%></span>
    <%= range_field_tag :answer_team_4,params[:answer_team_4], in: 1..100, step: 1, class:"d-inline"%>
    <p class="mx-3 d-inline align-top"><span id='entreprenership' ><%=params[:answer_market_4]%></span></p>
    <p class="mt-3"><span class="text-color">5)</span> La startup possède plus de 2 dirigeants avec une complémentarité de compétence ?<span class="text-danger">*</span></p>
    <%if params[:answer_team_5].to_i == 1%>
      <%= label_tag :answer_team_5, "Oui" %>
      <%= radio_button_tag :answer_team_5, 1, true%><br>
    <%else%>
      <%= label_tag :answer_team_5, "Oui" %>
      <%= radio_button_tag :answer_team_5, 1%><br>
    <%end%>
    <%if params[:answer_team_5].to_i == 2%>
      <%= label_tag :answer_team_5, "Non" %>
      <%= radio_button_tag :answer_team_5, 2, true%>
    <%else%>
      <%= label_tag :answer_team_5, "Non" %>
      <%= radio_button_tag :answer_team_5, 2 %>
    <%end%>
    <p class="mt-3"><span class="text-color">6)</span> Combien de salariés employez-vous (Équivalent Temps Plein) actuellement ?<span class="text-danger">*</span></p>
